document_data.mainbody:
House JeggDralnoc was a Lolthite drow house of the city of Sschindylryn in the 15 century DR.
By the time of the Darkening in the mid-1480s DR, JeggDralnoc was near-extinct. The house had been almost destroyed by House Szind during a power struggle, and its members only survived hidden in the dark corners of the world.
During the Sschindylryn invasion of Eveningstar in the late 15 century DR, the house was much reduced in number
* Asta JeggDralnoc, a Chosen of Lolth.
* Galfriel JeggDralnoc, the last priestess of the house.
